 fraction enhancement in post-mergers,\nrelative to a stellar mass-matched control sample, would indeed be the natural\nresult of merging randomly drawn pairs from a parent population which exhibits\na declining gas fraction with increasing stellar mass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jan 2015 19:15:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
