pment of such a computational tool can\naid the preparation of optical sensors prior to fabrication, by preselecting\ndesired the optical properties of the resonator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Jan 2015 09:18:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 02:47:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Feb 2015 08:31:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2015 23:07:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
