 a typical $3$-hour sea state,\nsuggesting that the Andrea rogue wave is likely to be a rare occurrence in\nquasi-Gaussian seas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Jan 2015 15:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 18 Jan 2015 00:24:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 24 Jan 2015 03:28:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2015 17:40:35 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2015 19:00:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-10"}
